data.description: Timeless contemporary 4 BR, 3.5 BA Raised Ranch will captivate you from the minute you cross the threshold. Relish in a beautifully appointed and updated living space, transitioning into the dining area and eat-in kitchen. The warm primary en-suite transitions seamlessly through the dressing lounge, walk-in closets and tastefully placed entrance to the grand room harmonizes functionality & design. Boasting vaulted ceilings, kitchenette and spa-like bath with a jet jacuzzi tub, dressed in abundance of light through the austere picture window.     Dive into luxury with the unique, abstract-shaped pool. Paired with a spacious patio and entertainment zone, it's a masterpiece of relaxation and fun sitting on just under 2 acres.
